Author: Entemma
Text: Yogurt cups, dates, carrot sticks, pickles, chickpea peanut butter cookie dough (can be eaten with a spoon), frozen grapes, icesicles made with diet lemonade, rice cakes, baked apple cubes with cinnamon, canned peaches, marshmallows, premade soups/broths, cauliflower buffalo ”wings”, baked tomato cubes with seasoning, water chestnuts, overnight oats with berries... Hope you can find something nice among those ideas!
